		"description": "<p>You weave raw magic into a mundane physical object no larger than a 5-foot cube. The object must be of a form and material you have seen before. Using the object as a material component for another spell causes that spell to fail.</p>\n<p>The spell's duration is determined by the object's material. An object composed of multiple materials uses the shortest duration.</p>\n<p><strong><em>Cast at Higher Levels.</em></strong> The size of the cube increases by 5 feet for each slot level above 5th</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Table: Creation</strong></p>\n<table style=\"width: 55.3398%; height: 100.8px;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 53.4408%;\"><col style=\"width: 46.5592%;\"></colgroup>\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.8px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">Material</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">Duration</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.8px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">Vegetable matter</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">1 day</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.8px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">Stone or crystal</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">12 hours</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.8px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">Precious metals</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">1 hour</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.8px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">Gems</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">10 minutes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.8px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">Adamantine or mithral</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">1 minute</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
